This paper deals with image synthesis, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves semantic labeling, which is a subfield of computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of conditional generative adversarial networks (GANs) and loss functions suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) subcategories. Finally, the paper deals with image synthesis, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
